A comprehensive Audit Dashboard for a Motorcycle Accessories Shop designed to monitor sales, inventory, and operational performance in real-time.

This project focuses on improving business decision-making by providing clear insights into key metrics such as product sales, stock levels, revenue trends, and supplier performance. The dashboard helps identify fast-moving and slow-moving items, track inventory shortages, and ensure efficient stock management.

Built with a user-friendly interface, it enables shop owners and managers to quickly analyze data, detect anomalies, and optimize overall store operations.

Key Features:

📊 Sales and revenue tracking
📦 Inventory monitoring and stock alerts
🔍 Product performance analysis
📈 Trend visualization for better decision-making
🛠️ Simple and interactive dashboard design
